    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The primary validation result demonstrates MAPE of 8.3 % against the 15 % tolerance, and all predicted RH values remain below the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision that the CFD model can reliably identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for this Class II CPB device.",
